Market Segmentation (by Application)

Commercial Aircraft: The largest segment due to increasing global air travel and stringent deicing regulations.
Military Aircraft: Growing segment due to defense aviation needs in extreme climatic conditions.
General Aviation: Rising demand for private aircraft deicing solutions.
Market Segmentation (by Type)

Type I Fluids: Primarily used for deicing, offering fast-acting solutions with limited holdover time.
Type II Fluids: Designed for aircraft with slower takeoff speeds, providing longer-lasting anti-icing protection.
Type III Fluids: A hybrid between Type I and Type II, offering moderate holdover time.
Type IV Fluids: Advanced anti-icing fluids providing extended protection against ice formation.
